text: Sungul Snezhinsk, formerly known as Sungul Chelyabinsk is a Russian handball team located in Snezhinsk. They compete in the Russian Handball Super League. They have taken part in four European Cups since 2007. ==Accomplishments== *Russian Handball Super League: **Third Place : 2012 ==External links== * EHF Club profile * Club history Category:Sport in Chelyabinsk Oblast Category:Russian handball clubs
